# Tawjih V4 — Full Platform Audit

## 1. Backend API Health
- [ ] Backend container running
- [ ] All routers registered in main.py
- [ ] Health endpoint responds

## 2. Auth Flow (Critical)
- [ ] POST /api/auth/register — creates user + profile + gamification
- [ ] POST /api/auth/login — returns JWT tokens
- [ ] POST /api/auth/refresh — refreshes access token
- [ ] GET /api/auth/me — returns current user
- [ ] Duplicate email → 409
- [ ] Wrong password → 401

## 3. Onboarding Flow
- [ ] Step 1: Role selection (Lycéen, Universitaire, Master, Parent)
- [ ] Step 2: Academic info (BAC score, field)
- [ ] Step 3: Target countries selection
- [ ] Step 4: Target field of study
- [ ] Step 5: Language proficiency
- [ ] Onboarding completion → redirects to dashboard

## 4. Frontend Pages (19 pages)
- [ ] Landing (/) — stats, hero, features sections
- [ ] Login (/login) — form, validation, JWT storage
- [ ] Register (/register) — form, role selector, redirects
- [ ] Dashboard (/dashboard) — personalized, auth-gated
- [ ] Explore Programs (/explore) — 60 programs, filters, 🇲🇦 badges
- [ ] Scholarship Search (/scholarships) — 15 scholarships, filters
- [ ] Budget Calculator (/budget) — French labels, MAD, country select
- [ ] Roadmap List (/roadmap) — 5 templates, create roadmap
- [ ] Profile (/profile) — user data display
- [ ] Settings (/settings) — load/save settings
- [ ] Document Vault (/documents) — 6 templates, 5 checklists
- [ ] Community Hub (/community) — posts, trending, groups
- [ ] Visa Prep (/visa-prep) — 6 countries, Q&A, tips
- [ ] Housing Guides (/housing) — country tabs, city guides, MAD
- [ ] Marketplace (/marketplace) — 9 services, MAD pricing
- [ ] Language Learning (/learn) — 5 languages, exam badges
- [ ] Exam Prep Home (/prep) — BAC, IELTS, TCF, TOEFL
- [ ] Admin Dashboard (/admin) — stats, users, content tabs
- [ ] Admin Translations (/admin/translations) — translation editor

